{"tid":1793683,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得呢套超人玩具","createTime":"2019-12-22T14:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T14:08:26.000Z","uid":244876,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85a26cda58c7fc4e537aa4bc62e28a3230c01118","tid":1793683,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9z1ui8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9z1ui8.jpg&h=d1329f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，執屋個陣搵到個箱<br />\n入面係十幾年前既玩具<br />\n細個唔聽話比人收晒入箱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日突然搵返<br />\n睇返有好多回憶<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下，印象中應該唔知得咁少數量<br />\n有冇巴絲記得呢1 set野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印象中應該去到帝拿定佳亞個年代就冇了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日後如果見返都未必想再買一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畢竟睇超人個種期待己經冇左<br />\n睇返小學係90後最好既年代<br />\n好多野都好優質<br />\n<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得過去都要努力向前行<br />\n休息夠就記得有好多人等緊我地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c89b407986e412a58405396762ce2f0bb8f990e","tid":1793683,"uid":251336,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:45: